lyrics:
[Verse]
In a world of darkness, we sought the light
Through the age of enlightenment, we'd fight
Questioning beliefs that were long held tight
A revolution of the mind, shining bright

[Chorus]
Oh, the age of enlightenment, set us free
With reason as our guide, we'd find our decree
Oh, the age of enlightenment, let knowledge be
Illuminate our souls, for all the world to see
